# ðŸŽ¨ Brand Color Guidelines

This document defines the core brand color palette and their intended uses.

## Primary Colors

| Name           | Value                  | Usage Description           |
|----------------|------------------------|-----------------------------|
| Background 1   | rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) | Main background             |
| Background 2   | rgba(252, 244, 237, 1) | Secondary background        |
| Main Color     | rgb(124, 180, 107)     | Brand's primary identity    |
| Accent         | rgba(255, 69, 26, 1)   | Accent (used sparingly)     |
| Border/Shadow  | black                  | For borders and shadows     |

> Note: All colors should be used with accessibility and contrast in mind.
